menu "Charge-Point Demo Configuration"

config WIFI_SSID
    string "Default Wi-Fi SSID"
    default "my_wifi_ssid"
    help
        This is an optional default Wi-Fi SSID used when no
        credentials are stored in NVS yet. Using Kconfig for
        this value makes it easy to change per build without
        touching the C source code.

config WIFI_PASSWORD
    string "Default Wi-Fi password"
    default "my_wifi_password"
    help
        Optional default Wi-Fi password used when NVS does not
        contain stored credentials. Leaving this empty and using
        a proper provisioning flow later is also fine.

config MQTT_BROKER_URL
    string "MQTT broker URL"
    default "mqtt://broker.hivemq.com"
    help
        MQTT broker URI used by the demo application. You can
        change this to point at a local broker without changing
        any C code; only this Kconfig entry needs updating.

endmenu
